+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Mi5sC4DakjcKcyNQkP57tu","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good. Now I have full context. Let me make the key design decisions and proceed to implementation.\n\n**Design Decisions (Autopilot):**\n\nQ: File structure?\n→ Single `TimeTracker` class in `src/tracker.ts`, types in `src/types.ts`, export from `src/index.ts`\n  Reasoning: Simple, clean, meets the requirements without over-engineering.\n\nQ: Persistence strategy?\n→ Synchronous file I/O with JSON serialization, read on construction, write after every mutation\n  Reasoning: Simple, no async complexity, suitable for a CLI tool where file ops are fast.\n\nQ: Data model?\n→ Array of `TimeEntry` objects with `id`, `name`, `startTime` (ISO string), `stopTime` (ISO string | null)\n  Reasoning: Simple, JSON-serializable, easy to filter/sum.\n\nNow let's implement with TDD. First, invoke the TDD skill."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":331,"cache_read_input_tokens":22564,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":331},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"13b18e1c-f434-4d8c-8ae6-2c543d32a2c5","uuid":"77d26876-9da9-4fbd-8c57-188aa0790b67"}
